---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Get Involved
description: "Join The Fullest Project — sign up for our newsletter, contribute resources, spread the word, or support our mission to connect families in the disability community."
permalink: /get-involved/
---

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero-gradient text-white py-16 lg:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">Get Involved</h1>
    <p class="text-xl opacity-90 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      The Fullest Project grows stronger with every person who joins in. Whether you have a minute or a mission, here's how you can help families in the disability community find what they need — and add what you know.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Tier 1: Community (newsletter) -->
<section class="py-16 section-warm">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-3" aria-hidden="true">💛</div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Become part of the Fullest Community</h2>
      <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">
        Sign up for our newsletter and be the first to know about new resources, programs, and stories for the disability community. A few emails a month, no spam, unsubscribe anytime — just the newest additions to the directory, practical guides, and encouragement from families who understand.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="card p-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-center" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Join our community newsletter</h3>
      <form action="https://formspree.io/f/{{ site.formspree.newsletter }}" method="POST" class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3"
        data-newsletter data-worker-url="{{ site.adminWorkerUrl }}/newsletter">
        <label for="community-email" class="sr-only">Email address</label>
        <input type="email" id="community-email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required class="form-input flex-grow">
        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary whitespace-nowrap">Subscribe</button>
      </form>
      <p class="text-xs mt-4 text-center" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">
        We'll send a confirmation email first — click the link in it to finish signing up. We never share your address.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Tier 2: Contributor (add resources + browser button) -->
<section class="py-16">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-3" aria-hidden="true">🧩</div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Become a Fullest Contributor</h2>
      <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">
        The strength of The Fullest Project comes from each of you sharing the resources and information you know, so that everyone can benefit. Come across a program, service, website, or organization that supports individuals with disabilities and isn't in our directory yet? Add it. Every resource you share saves another family hours of searching.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Browser button box -->
    <div class="card p-8 mb-6" style="border: 2px solid var(--color-secondary);">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2 justify-center">
        <span class="text-3xl" aria-hidden="true">📌</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Get the browser button</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center mb-6" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">
        The easiest way to contribute is our one-click browser button. Find a great resource anywhere on the web? Click it to send it to us — quickly and in the moment, no copying or pasting.
      </p>
      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="/quick-submit/" class="btn-secondary no-underline text-lg px-8 py-4 inline-block">Get the Browser Button</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-center" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">
      Prefer to add one now? <a href="/submit-resource/" class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-secondary);">Submit a resource &rarr;</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Tier 3: Advocate (share) -->
<section class="py-16 section-cool">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-3" aria-hidden="true">📣</div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Become a Fullest Advocate</h2>
      <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">
        Share The Fullest Project with everyone you know in the community — friends, therapists, teachers, support groups… anyone who could benefit from the information this site is curating, and who could add their own knowledge to the bank for everyone's benefit. The more people who know about it, the more complete and powerful it becomes.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="card p-8 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-5" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Spread the word</h3>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center">
        <button type="button" id="share-copy" class="btn-primary">Copy link</button>
        <a href="mailto:?subject=A%20resource%20hub%20for%20the%20disability%20community&body=I%20thought%20you%20might%20find%20The%20Fullest%20Project%20helpful%20%E2%80%94%20a%20free%20directory%20of%20disability%20resources%2C%20programs%2C%20and%20community%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fthefullestproject.org"
           class="btn-secondary no-underline">Email a friend</a>
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthefullestproject.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
           class="btn-secondary no-underline">Share on Facebook</a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=A%20free%20directory%20of%20disability%20resources%2C%20programs%2C%20and%20community%3A&url=https%3A%2F%2Fthefullestproject.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
           class="btn-secondary no-underline">Share on X</a>
      </div>
      <p id="share-copied" class="text-sm mt-4 font-semibold hidden" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Link copied — thank you for sharing! 💛</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Tier 4: Supporter (donate) -->
<section class="py-16">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-3" aria-hidden="true">🤝</div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Become a Fullest Supporter</h2>
      <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">
        Donate to The Fullest Project to help maintain and expand our directory, create educational content, and increase awareness of and accessibility to these resources. Your donation keeps the website running ad-free and accessible to every family who needs it.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="card p-8 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Support the mission</h3>
      <p class="mb-6" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">
        Donations are processed securely through Every.org. You can make a one-time gift or set up a recurring donation.
      </p>
      <a href="/donate/" class="btn-primary no-underline text-lg px-8 py-4 inline-block">Donate to The Fullest Project</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
// Copy-link share button
(function() {
  var btn = document.getElementById('share-copy');
  var msg = document.getElementById('share-copied');
  if (!btn) return;
  btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
    var url = 'https://thefullestproject.org';
    function done() { if (msg) msg.classList.remove('hidden'); }
    if (navigator.clipboard && navigator.clipboard.writeText) {
      navigator.clipboard.writeText(url).then(done).catch(done);
    } else {
      var t = document.createElement('textarea');
      t.value = url; document.body.appendChild(t); t.select();
      try { document.execCommand('copy'); } catch (e) {}
      document.body.removeChild(t); done();
    }
  });
})();
</script>
